Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這個星期天你們都有什麼計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個禮拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要大家一起出去逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 麻音碳 是不是有什麼簽名會來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步小P要發售新作了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠也要去玉響幫忙做新的甜品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去參觀志保美小姐的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛道歉 沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒什麼要緊事 你們不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家做自己想做的事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 堂鄉叫我過去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別叫我薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確跟平常不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開發新的香調果然還是要有百花香比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:04:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說試試超級奇怪的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣椒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在一點點地向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠是做甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的就是正義
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪是拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音…有太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我決定不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做香料？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳香師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星期天我又想跟大家一起去小小秘境探險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:50.22,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道去哪兒好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家星期天都排滿了重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就日期另外再定 先幫我決定候選地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得附近的的場町和三喜神社不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事已經用不著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在忙著自己的事 別去打擾她們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小薰我們先去看看怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這個星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:06:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐說如果你願意的話要不要一起來見習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果你願意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是在意昨天的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 那個 願意的話要不要一起去簽名會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不討厭排隊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我沒有…這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰碳星期天的安排決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟奶奶說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來幫忙做甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責品嚐 品嚐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有吸引力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天我得陪姐姐一起去小小秘境探險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家來邀請我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人是桃貓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟小啪說過今天有點忙要先回去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我早上不是就說了別在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連小啪碳和麻音碳都很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為薰碳不是平常的薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟平常一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給佐代美姐姐打了電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說薰碳拒絕了小小秘境探險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而還邀請了我們 差點就被拉去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼會沒關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 如果你有什麼心事就跟我們說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你們這麼說 真的什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 就算叫你薰碳你也完全不吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管什麼跟傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一直跟你在一起所以一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你別管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fight
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭屁小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂怎麼了 已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煽風點火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在拍什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意識到要贏過小啪姐的溫情照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能從拍攝人類真實的表情入手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我要成為這小鎮的戰地攝影師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後贏過小啪姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 你們不用介意 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿了憤怒的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是想跟平常一樣就越是彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓大家擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 可以一起洗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.75,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天乃理惠打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 不要瞎多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我說錯什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那倒沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 為什麼你也進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾這樣也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一樣把泡泡做成比基尼的樣子玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,—然後、星期天—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了不用介意的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在乘電車去吳市的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步小P的新書真是期待 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好今天是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到專業攝影師工作 有點緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我學會了甜品的做法 下次做好了給你吃個飽 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這就是我想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動的話就用裝在這水槍裏的竹醋襲擊你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:50.77,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小知識 竹醋液是將蒸燒竹子時冒出的煙液化後的東西 很臭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說行的時候就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我並不討厭竹醋液的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個太強烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是效果超群啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚也光滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這個有點難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 進去裏面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說去探險的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是玉響的驚喜作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是next surprise噢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是覺得小薰有點奇怪 想著難道是有煩惱之類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而聚在一起的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐召集的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發了短信後發現大家都想著相同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不要幹那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都很擔心小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都說沒什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛 薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠 要拿那個出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我來裝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的 請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 那個味道太強烈了 別拿進來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是香草蛋糕和奶奶自製的熱柑橘汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香草是檸檬草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它還用了幾種能提神的香草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠想讓小薰精神起來而想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾你工作真抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到好主意還要感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 薰碳吃了快精神起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不想你這樣不利落的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你變回平時的小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不用勉強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.97,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道自己想做的事情是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然做百花香很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道能否像大家一樣將來也一直做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮各種事的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變得不知道其實自己想做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想著不能讓這種半途而廢的自己妨礙大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻反而讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還添了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我也有過這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然喜歡拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偶爾會想這是真正想做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂雖然不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是漫畫家果然也不錯之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪樣都不是嗎之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想的時候也有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這薰碳混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠怒髮衝冠模式發動中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中途放棄什麼的都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有想做的事情很糟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不覺得是妨礙和麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來 薰碳老是想著周圍的事想太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是想周圍的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 無所謂了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰碳你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼兒園時去BAMBOO JOY遠足那時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我早上開始就不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不想錯過期待已久的遠足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就勉強參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不臭噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.42,0:16:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我用了你一直很珍惜的紙巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有薰碳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那次遠足只會變成痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使到現在 那天的事也是特別的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你吃蛋糕 卻說嘔吐的事 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有過那種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 以前開始小薰就給了我很多特別的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有小薰在的話 我就能安心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像魔法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 因為小薰是魔法美少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法美少女薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 知道自己想做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上收到大家「我出門了」的短信的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使大家在不同的地方做著不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是在某處相連著的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺變得很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛才說不想妨礙大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讀了收到的短信之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:49.91,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（From:麻音 Sub：到達～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:49.91,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在到店裏了 果然好多人啊 我現在開始去排隊 啊 這之前先去買點吃的東西吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家能一起幹一件事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣想到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:53.16,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（From：小啪 Sub：在車站等待中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:53.16,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在竹原站等志保美小姐會合中 因為早到了 去拍下車站周圍吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起幹一件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.27,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（From：乃理惠 Sub：集中精神加油！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.27,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 看到材料興奮起來了 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 然後終於想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.19,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（From：小啪 Sub：攝影現場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:18:00.19,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在坐電車前往 也許是小薰也去過的地方 到了的話發照片給你）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在可以說一下想大家一起做的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏這裏 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是小小秘境探險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我發表了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:20.37,neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的展覽（暫定）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的展覽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將現在的我們所能做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所想的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所感受到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦率地展現出來的展覽會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪的話是至今所拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃理惠的是甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.27,0:18:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音是口笛直播
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的照片 展覽那種東西沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的口笛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要展現現在的努力就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好呢 我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是問題是場地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場地也決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏的話很完美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實已經讓爸爸確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12月30日的話可以隨便用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了之後的行動力依舊很強啊 薰碳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是繼承了你姐的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家全部是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺傳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的展覽 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼難得就試試干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是只有現在的我們才能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後即使什麼改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和大家在一起的事實是不會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留下現在能做的一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看著志保美小姐工作時想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍出能讓很多人看到而拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是很厲害的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得自己的照片還差很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想著能在我們的展覽讓很多人看到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就漸漸興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.96,0:21:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音碳的音樂舞台是這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後圍放著小啪碳的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是薰碳的百花香和我的甜點櫃檯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由小薰策劃的我們的展覽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想像不到會變成怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起辦成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一天一定會變成特別的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數次迷惘 止步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然夢想的去向也許何時會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們的現在就在於此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的展覽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.30,0:22:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.82,0:22:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重視衝擊性
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而馬上試做了新作的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.64,0:24:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用硬嗜喱裝飾的傾力之作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.69,0:24:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.33,0:24:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 玉響~hitotose~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.24,0:24:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「聖夜的故事」
